             "<li><strong>You help make life-saving medicines.</strong> Plasma can't be synthesized in a lab &mdash; it's used to make therapies for immune disorders, hemophilia, burns, and trauma. Your donation has a genuine medical purpose.</li>"
             "<li><strong>Free basic health screening every visit.</strong> Centers check your protein, hematocrit/iron, blood pressure, pulse, and temperature each time. It's not a substitute for a doctor, but regular donors sometimes catch issues like low iron early.</li>"
